  "instructions": [
    "heat the ttukbaegi-earthenware-cook over medium heat",
    "add the grape seed oil and let it simmer for 2 minutes",
    "add the chopped onion and sauté for 3-4 minutes until translucent",
    "add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute until fragrant",
    "add the petit pois, ground cumin, ground coriander, cayenne pepper, and salt. Stir well to combine",
    "add the lemon juice and stir to combine",
    "warm the ti-leaf wraps in a dry pan over medium heat for 1-2 minutes",
    "assemble the wraps by spooning the petit pois mixture onto the center of each wrap and topping with chopped walnuts"
